TSBlock()

A TimeSeries Block to process one timeseries

dblock = DataBlock(blocks=(TSBlock, CategoryBlock),
                           get_x=ColReader(x_cols),
                           get_y=ColReader('target'),
                           splitter=RandomSplitter(0.2))
